    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**1. Objective**"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "oaBoXuDvbuqv"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "The objective of this analysis is to determine whether the Air Conditioning unit available in the Heat Engine Laboratory can:\n",
        "\n",
        "1)Cool 40 milk containers from 40°C to 15°C within 2 hours.\n",
        "\n",
        "2)Maintain the milk at 15°C for approximately 24 hours."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "QPSwhwJWbwIu"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# ── GIVEN DATA ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
        "# You can change these values if your data is different\n",
        "\n",
        "n_containers   = 40       # Number of milk containers\n",
        "m_milk         = 5        # Mass of milk per container (kg)\n",
        "m_Al           = 2        # Mass of aluminium container (kg)\n",
        "c_milk         = 4000     # Specific heat of milk (J/kg·K)\n",
        "c_Al           = 921.1    # Specific heat of aluminium (J/kg·K)\n",
        "T_initial      = 40       # Initial temperature (°C)  ← worst case\n",
        "T_final        = 15       # Target temperature (°C)\n",
        "t_cooling      = 2 * 3600 # Cooling time in seconds (2 hours = 7200 s)\n",
        "\n",
        "print('Given Data Summary')\n",
        "print('='*45)\n",
        "print(f'  Number of containers       : {n_containers}')\n",
        "print(f'  Mass of milk / container   : {m_milk} kg')\n",
